cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.CY, cs.HC. 

The paper discusses the use of AI in art, which suggests that it belongs to the cs.AI sub-category. The topics of autonomy and authenticity are related to computer graphics (cs.GR) and computer vision (cs.CV), respectively. The topic of authorship is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and the topic of intention is related to cybernetics (cs.CY).
